## svglover

Source: https://github.com/globalcitizen/svglover
License: GPL-3.0
Local path: lib/svglover.lua
Modifications: Yes (see below)

This library is licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0.
The full GPL-3.0 text is available at:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt

Modifications made for LOVE 12.0 and Lucide icon compatibility:

1. \_colorparse: Added "currentColor" handling (returns white 1,1,1,1
   so callers can tint dynamically via love.graphics.setColor).
2. load: SVG root element attributes (fill, stroke, stroke-width,
   stroke-linecap, stroke-linejoin) are now parsed and injected into
   the root parent for proper CSS-style inheritance to child elements.
3. \_elementsfunctions["line"]: New handler for <line> SVG elements
   (x1, y1, x2, y2 attributes with stroke rendering).
4. \_elementsfunctions["rect"]: Added rx/ry attribute parsing for
   rounded corner rectangles.
5. \_inherited_attributes: Added stroke-linecap and stroke-linejoin.
6. \_gensubpath: Replaced LOVE 11 stencil API calls
   (love.graphics.stencil, love.graphics.setStencilTest) with direct
   polygon fill, as these functions were removed in LOVE 12.

